de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.transform.germanet
Class SemanticClassLabelExtractor

java.lang.Object
  de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.transform.germanet.SemanticClassLabelExtractor

public class SemanticClassLabelExtractor
extends java.lang.Object

This class offers methods for extraction of semantic class labels of LexUnit and Synset instances.
Instance of this class parses the names of GermaNet 7.0 files (semantic labels) and determines the LexUnits and Synsets contained in the file for which the semantic label applies.

Author:
Zijad Maksuti, Judith Eckle-Kohler
